title: ranked issue
body: i still have not receive my rank stuf... whats the problem???

replies.body: There was a [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#eune) over the last few days that rewards weren't finished distributing.  That seems to be gone now, so rewards should be finished being sent out.  If you haven't received yours yet, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).  We'll be happy to look into your issue individually!
